Title: Relates to establishing the MWBE Center within empire state development corporation
Summary: Establishes the MWBE Center within the empire state development corporation to make the services of the division of minority and women's business development accessible in-person in cities with a population of one million or more and to provide information assistance and technical support relating to certification.

ActClause: AN ACT to amend the economic development law, in relation to establishing the minority and women-owned business enterprise center within empire state development corporation
